{"type": "article", "id": 20561, "title": "像UFO的花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-12T07:13:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000413SFjWiAauQzLoZ64M.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个花瓶很有未来感，有点像一个 UFO。它是将两个倒立的三角锥重叠起来的，用三角架固定，最上面放了一个小盖子。通常将这类花瓶归为 “tulip Vases”一类。花朵沿着上下两圈的圆孔插进去，可以让花朵有层次感，搭配花瓶上蓝色的渲染的小点，很素雅，设计者来自荷兰，售价 355.15 美元，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/space-vase-blue-dots-edition/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000411ogCuHUEmnekcyKvh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49787234\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000412gObh3kxfWdB1DNnK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49787234\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000412eLk1rPcGvElCwFX8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.72659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}